<span id="freeTextContainer2664465139753823762">I LOVE JOSEPH CONRAD. I don&apos;t even know... there&apos;s just something about his writing that makes my brain happy. <br/><br/>I generally hate seafaring stories, but his are so much more than that. There&apos;s so much depth to his writing, and so much insight into the human psyche. Also, I have yet to read an author who does a more convincing oral-narration voice.<br/><br/>Also also... the man didn&apos;t even learn English until he was an adult. How he then managed to write in English with more finesse than 99% of English-speak</span>
